{"tid":4410,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日搭地鐵 有個學生妹無啦啦叫我個名","createTime":"2016-11-26T13:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T07:49:42.000Z","uid":25520,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0abaad096bb72ce4776d9ae71653d300422e17","tid":4410,"uid":25520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果陣佢同我企到好近<br />\n佢：xxx (我個名）喂 xxx<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (心諗我都唔識佢）<br />\n佢：你唔記得我呀？<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我成程車都冇應過佢 佢下個站就落左車<br />\n之後臨落車前 我見佢都幾靚 即刻問佢叫咩名<br />\n佢俾左佢條扎頭繩我 同埋講左佢個名俾我知<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知點個女仔會識我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我明明唔識佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw個女仔幾靚"},{"pid":"b91757cb97248d706ab504f0c755932f2b50452e","tid":4410,"uid":25520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:22:30.000Z","msg":"btw我已經唔記得左佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想係facebook揾佢都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d561c4db581b4dbe7a8013698dc8b3187043c7","tid":4410,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"你係 瀧？<br />\n佢好似叫三葉呀"},{"pid":"9d3f8777cedd9553a4d659e1c2f884f6f0583750","tid":4410,"uid":13725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-26T13:25:11.000Z","msg":"你的名字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed764a0bc6ab66a50797f58e54483869519b67b"